(15, 'Dead Prom Queen', 'I come out of my custom toe pincher all in Black Velvet, as a Zombie Promo Queen come to life to tease, strip . I then crawl back in and then surprise moment (secret)before I close the lid.', 0, 0, '2014-08-31 13:37:57', '2014-08-31 13:37:57'),
(16, 'Longing', 'Longing is about lust. Though equally as painful, there is something exquisite feeling about reaching for someone who is not quite there.  It is the moments where we can almost touch them, those moments of ecstasy, that keep us reaching.  I grasp at articles of clothing throughout the number, hoping to feel something real. They are, however, not stable enough to hold on to. Stability lies in releasing these things I hold on to and finding stability within.', 1, 0, '2014-09-02 05:14:16', '2014-09-11 04:55:57'),
(17, 'Porn Theatre', 'While attending the showing of a film, Maggie gets swept up in the...story. A piece which goes from up-tempo to slow and sensual, it features chair dancing, self touch, and some really big hair. ', 1, 0, '2014-09-08 01:12:43', '2014-09-08 20:19:59'),
(18, 'Sober', 'classic inspired boa routine with a bit a fierceness, floor work, and sparkle.', 1, 0, '2014-09-12 03:03:59', '2014-09-12 03:03:59'),
(19, 'Proud Mary', 'The act is an burlesque impersonation of Tina Turner. I sing and burlesque at the same time.\r\n\r\nOnly requires a mic on a mic stand front and center. Cleanup at end.', 1, 0, '2014-09-15 01:46:07', '2014-09-15 01:48:48'),
(20, 'Housewife''s Revenge', 'A demure housewife has had enough of her husband’s abuse and decides to reclaim her own life by taking his.', 1, 0, '2014-09-16 23:44:50', '2014-09-16 23:45:41'),
(21, 'Test vendor betty', 'betty tests vendors', 0, 0, '2014-09-21 03:18:25', '2014-09-21 03:18:25'),
(22, 'Cancan', 'Each Cardio-Cancan class starts with a ballet based warmup and stretching. Then we go over specific steps and techniques for cancan kick lines, traveling steps and turns. Finally, get your heart pumping with flirty cancan choreography! It’s so much fun, you won’t even realize you are working out!  ALL LEVELS OF FLEXIBILITY AND DANCE EXPERIENCE WELCOME!  This class has been designed to provide an introduction to classic ballet techniques in a comfortable environment for those who have never taken formal dance classes before. At the same time, experienced dancers will enjoy the sense of play, enjoyment and sensuality in the class, which can be hard to find in many traditional ballet studios.', 1, 0, '2014-09-22 02:38:03', '2014-09-22 02:38:03'),
(23, 'Baby''s On Fire', 'This act is to Die Antwoord''s "Baby''s On Fire" and is a silk fan dance.  The act is very high paced and the costume is entirely yellow, orange, and red.  The video is from a one of the first times performing this act and I have been developing and performing it for about six months now.  ', 1, 0, '2014-09-22 02:42:41', '2014-09-22 02:45:51'),
(24, 'Classic(Rock)', 'An act with a classic look and feel, but a very non-traditional music choice.  There are no presets for this act, and only costume pieces/isis wings to clear at the end.  ', 1, 0, '2014-09-23 01:04:59', '2014-09-23 01:06:17'),
(25, 'Killing Floor', 'Classic Burlesque act to a Garage Blue song, merging neo and classic together.', 1, 0, '2014-09-23 03:50:09', '2014-10-20 20:58:12'),
(26, 'Booty and the Geek', 'Spandex Booty Shorts and playsuits', 1, 0, '2014-09-23 16:22:02', '2014-09-23 16:25:19'),
(27, '*~striptease~*', 'I''ll probably take my clothes off or something', 0, 0, '2014-09-23 21:42:04', '2014-09-23 21:42:04'),
(28, 'What the Hell is Isadora Duncan Dance?', 'Are you a dancer?  A non-dancer?  Have you heard of Isadora Duncan?  Come learn the basic concepts of Isadora Duncan dance and find out why she is one of the "mothers of modern dance."   Learn the underlying movements, exercises, and basic Duncan "vocabulary" moves.  Isadora Duncan was falling out of her Grecian tunics  and dancing barefoot in the days of corsets and long skirts and her sensuality and stage presence were renowned. Wear comfortable clothes for dancing and no shoes or socks only please!  ', 1, 0, '2014-09-24 15:25:15', '2014-09-24 15:25:16'),
(29, 'My Real Name Is', 'Panel discussing the use of stage names and personas and the risks/problems of being forced to use your real identity.   How do social media restrictions harm us and benefit us?  How can we move to marketing and outreach methods that rely less on social media or is that a new standard that we must deal with?  Is it effective to switch social networks when our customer base is left behind on the old one?', 1, 0, '2014-09-24 15:30:51', '2014-09-24 15:30:51'),
(30, 'Inspired Not Copied', 'What inspires you as a performer?  How do you make sure it is inspiration and not a copy?  Where do you draw the line and how do you know when you have crossed it?  ', 1, 0, '2014-09-24 15:36:31', '2014-09-24 15:36:31'),
(31, 'Teasing Your Chakras', 'A sexy, flexy, yoga-lesque routine that is part yoga, playing right into the hands of those who love women in yoga pants, and is all burlesque-style fun!\r\n\r\nWhat starts out as a normal yoga practice suddenly gets sexy with a glittery yoga mat, the removal of clothing, a half-naked head-stand, an  upside down bra removal and Namaste in pasties.   ', 1, 0, '2014-09-29 17:16:00', '2014-10-09 03:05:29'),
(32, 'S', 'S', 0, 0, '2014-09-30 02:08:04', '2014-09-30 02:08:04'),
(33, 'Dang Tourist! ', 'Cherie Nuit brings the absurdity of tourist season to the down-and-dirty beat of the Scissor Sisters!\r\n\r\nAct Synopsis: A tourist, caught off guard by her sudden crowd exposure, learns how to shake and shimmy. Whilst dancing with her maps (which she has rigged as fans!) she reveals her dedication to tourist season: a fanny pack bra, fanny pack panties, and hidden sunscreen for those sweltering days.A final reveal includes a big surprise: her fanny-pack crotch panties have a mind of their own and want to join in on the fun (they lip sync the song lyrics). \r\n\r\nThis is a very silly, over-the-top campy act that is best witness, not described :) (see video attached, recommended to watch in full screen) \r\n\r\n**VIDEO NOTE: This was part of a large scale production, the folks who are on screen from 0 sec- 14 sec are NOT featured in this act!!!', 1, 0, '2014-09-30 21:05:37', '2014-09-30 21:13:58'),
(34, 'Bait ', 'A sexy, sultry, ultra "glam" (and semi abstracted) take on "bait". \r\n\r\nThis semi-classic/semi-neo act explores the concept of bait and compares it to women''s bodies. Cherie Nuit reels the audience in just as one does a fish. Surprises include a shimmy belt made out of shiny lures, extendable fishing lures (and some fun audience participation!) ultra sexy floor work, and finally a fish that gets pulled out her "lady bits" area (optional, depending on nudity laws at the venue. **Note: No actual nudity will be shown, merkin and pasties stay on the entire time) ', 0, 0, '2014-09-30 21:29:43', '2014-09-30 21:29:43'),
(35, 'Black Swan', 'A summary of the last half hour of the film Black Swan/an interpretation of Swan Lake this act features the worst ballet ever put on stage and ends in Maggie''s theatrical death. It''s a comedy. ', 1, 0, '2014-10-02 17:12:09', '2014-10-02 17:13:24'),
(36, 'The Art of the Performer Bio', 'Do you find yourself in a panic when asked for a bio? Not sure what to say, or how much you should say? This class will introduce you to the genre of the performer bio, and provide a method for creating a stockpile of bios for various audiences – from festival producers, to fans, to potential bookers. The bio is a critical tool for performer’s self-presentation, and this class will instruct students on how to craft engaging biographies that maintain a consistent persona across multiple platforms. Bring a notebook and a pen.', 1, 0, '2014-10-02 21:17:11', '2014-10-02 21:17:11'),
(37, 'Funky Fans: Going Beyond the Feathers', 'Feather fans are the beautiful, elegant epitome of classic burlesque in the minds of most laypeople. But one of neo-burlesque''s most engaging properties is the way it can transform the classic into the clever and creative. This class will introduce students to construction techniques for non-feather fans, so that they can learn to make fans out of anything from flowers to porno magazines to Christmas ornaments to human hair! The class will also consider adapting classic fan moves for non-feather fans, as well as a offer theories for creating engaging fan reveals with non-feather fans. This class will be taught in a demo and movement format - we won''t make any fans in class, but you will walk away knowing how to!', 1, 0, '2014-10-02 21:23:31', '2014-10-02 21:23:31'),
(38, 'Candy Girl Did A Bad Bad Thing', 'Starts out cute and sassy with playful elements and candy props to Candy Girl, then transitions to darker, sexier classic strip tease to Baby did an Bad Bad thing.', 1, 0, '2014-10-04 22:02:18', '2014-10-14 15:15:39'),
(39, 'Daria down n'' dirty', 'I come out to the Daria show Intro("standing on my neck"), All I need for my props/set-up are my chair with a newspaper on it. Music medley changes from "just a girl" and "Suck my kiss" (all the 90''s goodness that is Daria!, while Daria confesses her love/hate for Trent.(*In the video what is happening off-camera, putting my glasses on someones face, and pulling my boots off on someones chair/lap.*)', 1, 0, '2014-10-06 14:53:53', '2014-10-06 15:10:09'),
(40, 'DAX', 'DAX (Jadzia)from Star Trek DS9-walks out, music changes and she then takes the "Venus drug", and after stripping down, ultimately cuts the symbiont(Dax)out of her! Jadzia can not survive without Dax so she falls to the ground to her death at the end.\r\n\r\n**I have a video but do not currently have access to the URL, can send later**', 0, 0, '2014-10-06 15:09:32', '2014-10-06 15:10:22'),
(41, 'Lady Courtesan', 'Vivian Vice is quite the lady in this red  hot classic striptease, the lady Courtesan \r\n\r\nI will be performing with a chair or piece  or furniture. My costume is all red and will strip out of corset, skirt and gloves , I may add a boa, and add to costume,and dance I am always revising and working on my dances!', 1, 0, '2014-10-06 15:57:05', '2014-10-21 00:30:56'),
(42, 'Jungle Book', 'Neo-comedy. No set up required. Clean up is 1 mask, 1 body-suit, 2 gloves, and 2 shoes.', 1, 0, '2014-10-06 16:02:38', '2014-10-06 16:02:38'),
(43, 'Flirty & Fit', '\r\nFirm and tone your entire body in this flirty and fun exercise class! Each class will include cardio and strengthening exercises that emphasize the physicality, flexibility and technique used by burlesque performers! Not a burlesque performer? That''s ok! This full body workout will firm and tone you in all the right places.\r\n\r\nParticipants should wear form fitting exercise clothes, comfortable shoes, and bring a towel and water bottle.', 1, 0, '2014-10-06 16:05:34', '2014-10-06 16:05:34'),
(44, 'Ballet for Burlesque', 'Ballet for Burlesque is a Ballet technique barre-based course that focuses on balance, grace, and strength for the entire body using exercises pulled from the classical ballet repertoire. This course is taught by Matt Finish, former soloist with Les Ballets Trockadero de Monte Carlo.\r\n\r\nParticipants should wear form-fitting dance wear and ballet shoes.', 1, 0, '2014-10-06 16:07:01', '2014-10-06 16:07:01'),
(45, 'A Thing for You', 'Classic burlesque act of a palm tree lady coming to life to tease you!\r\nSince the video was made I added a prop wooden crate. ', 1, 0, '2014-10-06 21:57:14', '2014-10-06 21:59:07'),
(47, 'Improvisational Character Development and Movement', 'using movement based improvisational techniques to strengthen the emotional and character aspects of Burlesque performances.\r\nClass would include movement based exercises as well as acting technique and performance coaching.', 1, 0, '2014-10-07 16:59:37', '2014-10-07 16:59:56'),
(48, 'Dance Improvisation', 'We are dance based performance artists, everything we do is entirely improvisational and in the moment, while the theme to our act will be similar (the wings and the transformation). The movement will be entirely different, and depending on the stage we like to incorporate the audience into the piece, through emotional and sometimes physical elements, creating a one of a kind experience for all.', 1, 0, '2014-10-07 23:47:44', '2014-10-07 23:47:44'),
(49, 'Expecto Patronum! ', 'Harry: "And how do you conjure it?"\r\nRemus: "With an incantation, which will work only if you are concentrating, with all your might, on a single, very happy memory."\r\n\r\nThis is an act based on the Patronus Charm from the Harry Potter series. In the lore of the story, casting a patronus is difficult as it requires you to focus on your most positive memory. By casting myself as a patronus I embody positivity and joy, and as a fat woman I attempt to make the audience feel the tie between my large form and joy, thus asking them to examine their own dearly held body prejudices, and hopefully begin to change them. I invite the audience to find my abundant flesh very, very sexy--a idea the larger society is slow to accept.\r\n\r\nThe goal is to reach the shy chubby girl in the audience, and to empower her to know that if she finds me beautiful that she must also examine herself and discover that she is so, so beautiful. I attempt to be her mirror. \r\n\r\nA simple joyful piece, I transform from tightly bound and corseted (like our puritanical society) to bold, open, wild, and radiant. \r\n\r\nSet up required: None. \r\nPick up required: Cloak, corset, dress, bra, panties.   ', 1, 0, '2014-10-08 22:42:02', '2014-10-08 23:02:40'),
(50, 'Expecto Patronum! ', 'Harry: "And how do you conjure it?"\r\nRemus: "With an incantation, which will work only if you are concentrating, with all your might, on a single, very happy memory."\r\n\r\nThis act is based on the Patronus Charm from the Harry Potter series. A Patronus is a difficult spell to cast, as in the lore of the story it can only be cast by focusing on your most positive memory. \r\n\r\nBy casting myself as the Patronus I embody joy and positivity, and as a fat woman I attempt to tie those powerful feelings of happiness and positivity to my larger form; showing the audience that they are tied, and asking them to examine their own closely held ideas and prejudices about bodies, and hopefully cause them to start to change those views. I invite the audience to find my abundant flesh very, very sexy--a idea the larger society is slow to accept. \r\n\r\nThe goal is to reach the shy chubby girl in the audience, and to empower her to know that if she finds me beautiful that she must also examine herself and discover that she is so, so beautiful. I attempt to be her mirror. \r\n\r\nA simple joyful act, I go from tightly bound and corseted to bold, open, wild, and radiant. \r\n\r\nSet up required: None\r\nPick up required: cloak, corset, dress, bra, panties. ', 0, 0, '2014-10-08 23:00:02', '2014-10-08 23:00:02'),
(51, 'Replicants', 'An acrobatic striptease with an element of Sci-fi. While technically "nerdlesque" this piece transcends borders. Even if you have never seen Bladerunner, you will enjoy the movement, costuming and and playful flare!', 1, 0, '2014-10-09 00:00:33', '2014-10-09 00:00:33'),
(52, 'Stretch and Strength For Contortion', 'Can''t touch your toes? Can you put your feet over your head no problem? Either way, this class is definitely for you. Come get a deep thorough stretch with Chicago''s Creature Contortionista, Dahlia Fatale. She will also walk you though a bit of anatomy and how to use some of your new found bendiness for fun choreographed tricks.', 1, 0, '2014-10-09 00:02:33', '2014-10-09 00:02:33'),
(53, 'Rock and Roll Chair', 'The top attended class from last year is back again! Chair are not just for sitting down. Bring out your inner rock and roll while learning chair dance moves that will surely wow an audience and make you feel great!', 1, 0, '2014-10-09 00:04:01', '2014-10-09 00:04:01'),
(54, 'Hit Me With a Hot Note', 'Highly energetic and full of Musical Theatre style dance, Hit Me With a Hot Note is a show stopping strip tease! I wanted to create a piece where my movement gets even bigger when I''m only in pasties to show a side of burlesque that is more athletic. \r\n\r\nThis is the number that won The Slipper Room''s Burlesque Idol in October in New York City. The early strip tease makes for a great opening number and gets the audience excited on the first note! \r\n\r\nNo props or additional clean-up in necessary. Can include audience interaction in small venues, or go without on larger stages.', 1, 0, '2014-10-09 17:44:20', '2014-10-09 17:46:32'),
(55, 'Heaven Knows', 'The act is a reverse strip tease. I play a voyeur who performs for a camera I notice in a room. The twist is that I''m only in the room because I''m the maid and I''m there to clean. ', 1, 0, '2014-10-11 03:23:07', '2014-10-11 03:23:07'),
(56, 'Roller Derby Chick', 'The act begins with me being a happy go lucky girl lacing up her skates (music: Brand New Skates Brand New Key by Melanie) As I get ready to start skating I cant even stand. I end up doing splits and all sorts of stuff in my efforts to skate. Eventually, I feel defeated and sit back down. The music switches (music: Roller Skate by Trooper)This is when my true roller girl breaks through. The more I remove the fiercer I get!', 1, 0, '2014-10-11 23:11:24', '2014-10-12 19:14:58'),
(57, 'Killer Queen', 'Marie Antoinette with a modern rock & roll twist. There will be cake!', 1, 0, '2014-10-12 13:20:43', '2014-10-14 15:15:23'),
(58, 'Neo dark cabaret', 'This is a Exotic combo class of Classical Burlesque meets Neo classic with theatrical cabaret moves, stage presence, With a dark edge Great for those who enjoy dancing to Other genres of music other then Classic and like to add Gothic or alternative styles to their repertoire ', 1, 0, '2014-10-12 20:27:55', '2014-10-12 20:27:55'),
(59, 'Tabasco!', '', 0, 0, '2014-10-15 21:24:26', '2014-10-15 21:24:26'),
(60, 'Generic 12 step meeting', 'I have been to a bunch of festivals and Cons recently and, noticed they offer this. It is very helpful to have for performers who attend a 12 step program that are so wrapped up in the festival that they can''t leave to find a meeting. So I am proposing that we bring the meeting to them. Host it just like one of the classes and, it will be generic so it will be welcoming to all 12 step program followers.\r\n\r\nPlease if this class does get accepted please do not publish my name as I wish to be anonymous. It is the way the program works.  ', 1, 0, '2014-10-15 23:23:56', '2014-10-15 23:23:56'),
(61, 'Pasties On The Cheap', 'Miss Bella La Blanc from Virginia for this special one-day/night-only work shop!\r\n\r\nBella''s workshop will show performers of all levels how to construct a pastie with different kinds of fabrics and materials so all budgets are met!\r\n\r\nBella will also show students how to make and keep permanent patterns for you nipple shape as well how to make unique shapes and patterns such as stars, hearts, etc!\r\n\r\nOf course...there will be tassels! Bella''s class will be covering how to attach a removable tassel and even how to MAKE a tassel!\r\n', 1, 0, '2014-10-15 23:25:55', '2014-10-15 23:25:55'),
(62, 'Regina/Queen Of The Night', 'This is Regina aka The Evil Queen from Once Upon A Time/Snow White.\r\n\r\nIt is her presenting her apple and enchanting it before she presents it to Snow and, she hopes for her demise. She is showing that she is the one who is the fairest of them all!! MUhahahaha.\r\n\r\nThe costume has also been updated. I have been touring with it for several months now.\r\n\r\nNOTE- This is the only Video I have of this # and I performed on a pulled Hamstring.. The show must go on right!', 0, 0, '2014-10-15 23:34:11', '2014-10-15 23:34:11'),
(63, 'Bella''s Tchotchkis', 'Hair Flowers, Fascinators, Mini Tophats, Pasties, and detachable handmade tassles', 0, 0, '2014-10-15 23:39:20', '2014-10-15 23:39:20'),
(64, 'Makeup Eraser', 'The Makeup Eraser removes ALL makeup with just water- including waterproof mascara and stage makeup. After your performance, take it all off- makeup that is, with the Makeup Eraser. No more toting oily makeup removers and wasting money on towelettes. Lasts 1,000 washes. As seen on NBC''s Today Show. ', 0, 0, '2014-10-16 00:43:19', '2014-10-16 00:43:19'),
(65, 'Makeup Eraser', 'The Makeup Eraser removes ALL makeup with just water- including waterproof mascara and stage makeup. After your performance, take it all off- makeup that is, with the Makeup Eraser. No more toting oily makeup removers and wasting money on towelettes. Lasts 1,000 washes. As seen on NBC''s Today Show. ', 1, 0, '2014-10-16 00:43:46', '2014-10-16 00:43:46'),
(66, 'Hello Dolly', 'This is my "signature" act. Inspired by Barbra Streisand''s character in the movie by the same name, this is a fun and upbeat act. My character starts out shy with the music quiet and slow and as the music builds, the character becomes more bold. Costume is yellow and gold with afeather headdress and I use a parasol for different reveals throughout the act.', 1, 0, '2014-10-16 18:46:42', '2014-10-16 18:46:42'),
(67, 'On Towards Greatness: Troupe Leadership Strategies', 'Do you ''rule'' your troupe with strict guidelines or is it more of a laissez-faire style? What types of written and/or legal documents - if any - do you require your members to sign and why?  What works and what just plain falls flat amongst leadership styles when managing a troupe full of burly ladies & gents? Come and hear what our panelists have to say about their many collective years of experience in managing successful troupes all across the country (and around the world)!', 1, 0, '2014-10-17 07:16:21', '2014-10-17 07:16:21'),
(68, 'Marlene''s Blues', 'A suit strip set to smoky jazz.', 1, 0, '2014-10-17 13:59:36', '2014-10-17 14:06:25'),
(69, 'Glorious Pasties', 'Rhinestoned pasties, underthings and other fine rhinestoned goods', 0, 0, '2014-10-18 16:44:37', '2014-10-18 16:44:37'),
(70, 'Clark Kent to Superman', 'This course will cover character development as a way of protecting your private life (wigs, make up, masks, personality, etc...) The importance of establishing an independent "performance" profile on Social media. Tips for protecting your private life from your performance persona, ways to keep tabs on and check up on your online presence. There will be a discussion portion where students can share tips and techniques, and a question & and answer portion. ', 1, 0, '2014-10-19 02:59:33', '2014-10-19 02:59:33'),
(71, 'Twerking in the Rain Bang ', 'Twerking in the rain is a mash up of the Todrick Hall parody of Singing in the Rain and the Big bang Theory theme song.  Howard Wolowitz leaves the company of his overbearing mother to enjoy a little romp in the rain. \r\n\r\nThe footage is an early draft I have made upgrades line it was first posted.', 1, 0, '2014-10-19 03:08:11', '2014-10-20 01:50:18'),
(72, 'this creature called woman', 'My performance will express the phases of a woman''s life...starting in childhood moving to the developing adolescence, becoming the emerging woman as the performance peaks when the confident middle aged voluptuous woman blossoms soon to transition into old age. This performance will express not only the woman''s physical changes in her body as she developes and ages but also express the intellectual changes too. My routine will use humor, also show a serious side, while we chronicle life''s travel with this creature we call woman!', 0, 0, '2014-10-19 05:52:59', '2014-10-21 07:26:18'),
(73, 'yoga for burlesque', 'Yoga is an essential exercise for strength flexibility and balance which are important elements of a performance dance and or routine. Come experience an introduction to various yoga postures a d then relish the relaxation of savasana.', 1, 0, '2014-10-19 07:11:46', '2014-10-19 07:11:46'),
(74, 'Liquid Lunch', 'I am a socialite that simply wants bigger and better martinis. Someone mentioned to me it was like Breakfast at Tiffany''s meets Alice in Wonderland. Watch as the drinks get bigger while the amount of clothing gets smaller. ', 1, 0, '2014-10-19 22:39:26', '2014-10-22 04:40:22'),
(75, 'Haunted', 'Start offstage as music begins.  Would like a Stage Kitten if possible to hand my discarded clothing to.  Chair in direct center of stage with back of chair to audience.  Simple, classic act w/boa to a Goth song with me in full body zombie/ghoul makeup.', 0, 0, '2014-10-20 04:06:04', '2014-10-20 04:06:04'),
(76, 'Fade Into You-oo-oo', 'I have taken :06 seconds of the act for the time limit and the video does show a costume malfunction. It is a nerdlesque act with classic elements. First 1/2 is a slower fan dance and the second upbeat sans fans till the reveal. It is in the character of Rogue from the X-men and is about longing and the desire to be able to touch.  No other props are used.', 1, 0, '2014-10-20 13:02:13', '2014-10-20 13:02:13'),
(77, 'Burlesque Hosting For Performers', 'Imagine this: \r\nYou''re surrounded by beautiful, strong, talented burlesque performers, and it''s your job to introduce each one of them to an eager crowd. As a performer, you understand the complexity of each act, but how do you prepare the audience for the show?\r\nIn this fun, interactive class, learn the steps to getting over public speaking anxiety, tightening transitions between each act, and bringing your own flair to the realm of burlesque hosting!', 1, 0, '2014-10-20 13:22:05', '2014-10-20 13:22:05'),
(78, '"Everybody''s Girl"', 'A brash, belted, flirty extravaganza in red and black, with live singing of "Everybody''s Girl" from the musical Steel Pier.\r\n\r\n(NOTE: The act in the video is my Pierrot act, which is so much fun, but sans singing)', 1, 0, '2014-10-20 13:38:28', '2014-10-21 02:09:41'),
(79, 'Nasty Naughty Boy', 'Striptease into a bathtub finishing with a champagne bath.  * NOTE: glitter bath is contained in the bath tub ( if tarp is needed for extra protection I can supply ) ', 0, 0, '2014-10-20 17:41:54', '2014-10-24 23:59:10'),
(80, 'Nasty Naughty Boy', 'Striptease into a bathtub finishing with a champagne bath.  * NOTE: glitter bath is contained in the bath tub ( if tarp is needed for extra protection I can supply ) ', 1, 0, '2014-10-20 17:46:08', '2014-10-20 18:04:59'),
(81, 'Under Your Skin', 'A classical chair dance routine with fun reveals and engaging the audience with glee. ', 1, 0, '2014-10-20 21:19:05', '2014-10-20 21:26:24'),
(82, 'Beauty Butler', 'Portable Makeup Organizer', 0, 0, '2014-10-20 22:45:14', '2014-10-20 22:45:14'),
(83, 'Big Boned Gal', 'A celebration for "big-boned" or "curvy" or "pleasantly plump" women. It''s a country-fied strip of the rural gal having fun and enjoying her body...inviting everyone to the party with her.\r\n\r\nIn more pedestrian terms, it involves a pretty straightforward strip with a hand fan and a little floor work. Costume is vintagey country.', 1, 0, '2014-10-21 01:59:38', '2014-10-21 01:59:54'),
(84, 'Not Gonna Strip Tonight', 'I come onto the mic saying I''m not going to strip and instead I am doing the next best thing: poetry. Then I recite a poem I''ve written about why I have decided to keep my clothes on these days -- and I perform it while undressing.\r\n\r\nBy the way, the costume has changed -- here is the updated outfit: http://artifuss.tumblr.com/post/99036889649/in-which-i-decide-to-do-away-with-a-glove', 1, 0, '2014-10-21 06:16:43', '2014-10-21 06:16:43'),
(85, 'Let''s Burn', 'This is one of my new acts, partially choreographed by Perle Noire. \r\n\r\nIt is best decribed as a classic, sultry, fan dance.\r\n\r\n**The cigarette is electronic.', 1, 0, '2014-10-21 19:17:01', '2014-10-21 19:22:07'),
(86, 'Race Car', '', 0, 0, '2014-10-21 21:55:11', '2014-10-21 21:55:11'),
(87, 'Coconut', 'Chair a bit upstage center with coconut and shaker placed next to it. Enter on music. Tyranna tries to figure out how to make her favorite drink with a lime and a coconut but the coconut won''t fit into the shaker. "Accidents" happen (there is no liquid involved). Strip down to grass skirt and coconut bra. After taking off coconut bra I realize that the limes were in the coconuts all along and exit offstage while music fades. Things left on stage are coconut, dress, head scarf, petticoat, and book.', 1, 0, '2014-10-21 22:36:30', '2014-10-21 22:42:15'),
(88, 'Weapons', 'I come out with a large dagger/knife in a little sheath and pull the sheath off with my teeth. I take off my gloves. Then there''s a moment in the video that you cannot see me, during which time, I am still visible on stage to the side as I have the stage kitten unzip the back of my dress. You can see the rest of the strip tease clearly in the video. I remove my dress, stockings, bra, and underwear. I strip down to pasties and a C string and carry the knife offstage.\r\n\r\nI use a stage kitten''s help to unzip the dress. I cue them by pointing straight at them and making a "come hither" motion at them. I also need a chair center upstage.', 1, 0, '2014-10-21 23:58:05', '2014-10-21 23:58:05'),
(89, 'Home Alone', 'Businesswoman arrives home from work in a huff, tired at the end of a long day, and discovers that she is home alone. She decides to take advantage of that by REALLY letting loose, having fun, and of course losing her clothes. Upbeat, fun, and lots of removals!', 1, 0, '2014-10-22 01:23:13', '2014-10-22 02:51:48'),
(90, 'Inside Out', 'I''m submitting for "Inside out" and would be more than happy to perform the routine I already have.  However, I am hoping to begin working on another routine and have it ready to go by February.  ', 1, 0, '2014-10-22 01:37:10', '2014-10-22 01:37:10'),
(91, 'Tiki Fan Dance', 'A fun tiki dance complete with fans and a tear away hula skirt!', 1, 0, '2014-10-22 01:59:15', '2014-10-22 02:32:03'),
(92, 'Summertime Mash Up', 'A steamy Summer afternoon leads to a festive fan dance.', 1, 0, '2014-10-22 02:02:02', '2014-10-24 01:53:55'),
(93, 'Tinkerbell', 'Tinkerbell is a woman scorned.  She loves Peter Pan and has spent years making him happy. Despite this, he is more interested in the other woman, Wendy Darling, for her traditional motherly qualities.  In this act Tinkerbell vents her betrayal and sexual frustrations.            ', 1, 0, '2014-10-22 02:17:41', '2014-10-22 02:47:31'),
(94, 'A Nerd''s Revenge', 'A nerdlesque inspired number where I''m caught ready a really good "nerdy" book while in my dorkiest attire. My character is a bit shy, but realizes that even she is pretty hot stuff. And reading is hot. ', 1, 0, '2014-10-22 02:35:54', '2014-10-22 02:35:54'),
(95, 'Box of Secrets', 'An electro-swing group act of corsets and canes.\r\nNote: different troupe members may replace others in the actual performance, but core choreography will be the same', 1, 0, '2014-10-22 02:54:38', '2014-10-22 02:54:39'),
(96, 'Lucy The Mooch', 'Classic bump and grind.', 1, 0, '2014-10-22 03:19:49', '2014-10-24 23:11:17'),
(97, 'Lucy The Mooch', 'Classic bump and grind.\r\n\r\n', 1, 0, '2014-10-22 03:26:27', '2014-10-22 03:26:28'),
(98, 'Keeping your Ecdysiast Books', '"I''m not in burlesque for the money." That''s fine, but, there is money involved, and we all need to keep track of it. \r\n\r\nClass topics will include opportunity costs, break even points, invoicing and what your accountant is looking for during tax season.\r\n\r\nTime permitting, advanced tax topics like depreciation and amortization will be covered.', 1, 0, '2014-10-22 10:31:18', '2014-10-22 10:31:18'),
(99, 'Dancing in Shoes You Shouldn''t Be Walking In', 'This class will help you conquer your fear of (shoe) heights. We will  examine the natural motion of walking and adapt it to a graceful and powerful presence in high heels.', 1, 0, '2014-10-22 10:36:25', '2014-10-22 10:36:25'),
(100, 'Handsewing 101: Fast and Easy Shimmy Belt Construction', 'In the process of introducing hand stitching technique, students will build their own simple shimmy belt. Topics will include proper selection of  needles, thread, and materials, as well as reinforcements, fasteners and a selection of basic stitches.', 1, 0, '2014-10-22 10:40:57', '2014-10-22 10:40:57'),
(101, 'That Serpent', 'Copperhead Snake sheds its skin', 0, 0, '2014-10-22 10:49:27', '2014-10-22 10:49:27'),
(102, 'That Serpent', 'Copperhead Snake sheds its skin', 0, 0, '2014-10-22 10:50:17', '2014-10-22 10:50:17'),
(103, 'CABARRET, Fit. ', 'CABARRET is a unique combination of barre and burlesque, strength and cardio, with lots of stretching incorporated to give you an incredibly effective workout.\r\n\r\nA disciplined strength training program combined with sexy cardio dance workout is FUN! Work at the barre translates to toned thighs, a sexy booty, tight abs and sculpted arms. Our cardio burlesque dance burns fat and calories.\r\n\r\nIn CABARRET, we celebrate our body. You leave each class empowered and centered, with strength and sass!\r\n\r\nPerfect for women seeking to use burlesque in fitness, or for empowerment!', 1, 0, '2014-10-22 11:29:32', '2014-10-22 11:29:32'),
(104, 'CABARRET Teacher Training', 'Perfect for burlesque dancers who are fitness or dance instructors! Provides a  legitimate, ACE (American Council on Exercise)-approved certificate and Continuing Education Credits. \r\n\r\nCABARRET is a unique combination of barre and burlesque, strength and cardio, with lots of stretching incorporated to give you an incredibly effective workout.\r\n\r\nA disciplined strength training program combined with sexy cardio dance workout is FUN! Work at the barre translates to toned thighs, a sexy booty, tight abs and sculpted arms. Our cardio burlesque dance burns fat and calories.\r\n\r\nIn CABARRET, we celebrate our body. You leave each class empowered and centered, with strength and sass!\r\n\r\nIn order to cover the entirety of the Teacher Training Curriculum, this class would have to be spread over all 3 days, with participants attending every session. While more than a usual conference workshop, this Teacher Training gives students the credentials and experience to leave a make money with the burlesque background. ', 1, 0, '2014-10-22 11:33:09', '2014-10-22 11:33:09'),
(105, 'Ballet for NonDancers', 'Former professional ballet and modern dancer CoCo LeBod leads you through a movement session meant to make the graceful, elegant movements of ballet accessible, even to non-dancers!\r\n\r\nGreat technique refresher for experienced dancers as well!', 1, 0, '2014-10-22 11:36:04', '2014-10-22 11:36:04'),
(106, 'volunteer bid: Roy Egbert', 'volunteer bid', 1, 0, '2014-10-22 16:08:08', '2014-10-22 16:08:08'),
(107, 'Creepy Magic Act', 'Setup: Table, black table cloth covering, "rabbit" under the table and flower trick (size of a wand) on table top. \r\n\r\n', 1, 0, '2014-10-22 17:55:23', '2014-10-22 18:25:47'),
(108, 'Boobs', 'Only set up I need is two grapefruits in a basket towards the front or back of stage. I''m not too picky. \r\n\r\nThis video is about the second time I performed it, and it is completely polished now and has much more rhinestones. ', 0, 0, '2014-10-22 18:00:23', '2014-10-22 18:01:13'),
(109, 'Synchronized Swimming: Burlesque for Mermaids!', 'A brief history of the sport of synchronized swimming will be given, from water shows, to Esther Williams, to its emergence as an Olympic Sport. Particular emphasis will be given to the costume and make-up choices of exceptional competitors and how to use these choices to inform burlesque routines. Students will then be given the opportunity to learn an actual synchronized swimming routine from the pool of the official Exposition hotel, the Hyatt Regency. Simple movements will be incorporated that will develop strength, poise, and will expand any physical fitness routine, regardless of body size or prior athletic ability. ', 1, 0, '2014-10-22 18:37:11', '2014-10-22 18:37:11'),
(110, 'Sixteen Candles', 'Note on video--includes introduction by World Famous *BOB*. \r\n\r\nThis act is a tribute to the John Hughes movie "Sixteen Candles". The act can be cut to run under 4 minutes by taking out part of the first song. The set up begins with a cake onstage with a picture of boy crush Jake Ryan sitting on the table. I enter the stage, see the cake and get depressed. Then I get excited when I then see (and make-out with) picture of Jake. I close my eyes and make a wish on the birthday cake, the music changes, and Jake Ryan (in blow up doll form) magically appears! I then take off the dress and clothes to hump the blow up doll, tassels twirling, then carry it off into the sunset.', 1, 0, '2014-10-22 18:46:52', '2014-10-22 19:09:59'),
(111, 'When You''re Good to Mana', 'When You’re Good to Mama is a live sung musical theatre trio with the ladies stripping each other. ', 1, 0, '2014-10-22 21:08:05', '2014-10-25 02:29:31'),
(112, 'The True Story of Mary Poppins', '', 0, 0, '2014-10-22 21:49:45', '2014-10-22 21:49:45'),
(113, 'Black In Bloom', 'I sadly do not have a video of my performance...\r\n\r\nAs the song starts, I am covered with black Isis wings. For some time, I dance around & peek parts of me out from the closed wings. \r\n\r\nAround minute 2:15 I "bloom." My wings open revealing a beautiful sheer black dress with strategically placed rhinestones (so as not to upset the burlesque gods) & I spread my wings & fly, and of course, offer my wholehearted BUMPS & GRINDS to the, hopefully, delighted audience. ', 1, 0, '2014-10-22 22:06:00', '2014-10-23 01:17:56'),
(114, 'Red', 'This is a classic burlesque routine. Consists of gloves, dress, corset and bra. ', 0, 0, '2014-10-23 01:52:30', '2014-10-23 01:52:30'),
(115, 'Red', 'This is a classic burlesque routine. Consists of gloves, dress, corset and bra. ', 0, 0, '2014-10-23 01:52:49', '2014-10-23 01:52:49'),
(116, 'Princess Tiana', 'This is my take on my favorite new Disney princess: Princess Tiana.  She holds a special place in my heart as it ties me to my Louisiana heritage.  Here I pay homage to the first African American Disney princess to show her sass and attitude!\r\nNotes about vid:  Video is from first time I performed this act.  Had a slight wardrobe malfunction but has since been fixed.  Also, not wearing as big of falsies....as it makes me look like my eyes are closed the entire time.  \r\nProps: None\r\nItems needing to be picked up:  magnolia flower, petal top, 2 gloves, "leaf" top, skirt with hoop skirt attached, corset, and bra.', 1, 0, '2014-10-23 03:50:52', '2014-10-23 04:18:38'),
(117, 'Be You', 'Rasa Vitalia presented her original work "Be You," a song written, choreographed, and created by Rasa Vitalia. The show is about the cycles of life and women''s liberation (esp in the Middle East). The show is divided into a narrative of several acts. Part #1 Creation of life: The Veil Dance. Part #2 Life''s Battles and Destruction: The Sword Dance. Part #3 Rebirth: the Rhythms of life: finger cymbals/zills dance. Part #4 Celebration: Dance Party. #5 Liberation: The reveal. \r\n\r\nVideo link  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C7n73Y3UV4E\r\n', 0, 0, '2014-10-23 16:57:20', '2014-10-25 00:02:02'),
(118, 'You Can Always Count on Me', 'You Can Always Count on Me is a live sung musical theater piece telling the woes of a good girl gone (not necessarily) bad. ', 1, 0, '2014-10-23 17:53:29', '2014-10-24 03:57:41'),
(119, 'The Devil''s Dancer', 'This is a classic bump n'' grind routine to a very modern dubstep song! I am a femme representation of Dionysos, the horned god of wine, ecstasy and wilderness.\r\n\r\nNote that the video shows a costume malfunction: the back panel ripped out at the beginning of the song, while it should have been taken off after the front panel!', 1, 0, '2014-10-24 06:10:39', '2014-10-24 06:10:40'),
(120, 'Mission: Illusion', 'The Double D Agent Luella Lynne''s mission in this performance is to enrapture her target with illusion.  The act is a slow reveal of black costuming changing to gold.  Items that change include the dress, bra, panties, and pasties.', 1, 0, '2014-10-24 16:19:01', '2014-10-25 02:06:48'),
(121, 'Scratch''s Test Act', 'THis is my act description', 0, 0, '2014-10-24 23:38:59', '2014-10-24 23:38:59');
